        <briefdescription>
<para>Initialize a ring buffer. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Sets up the control structure to point to the provided storage array.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
